VINTAGE Photo Booth Features

  • 2 hosts to help to guide guests through the experience
  • Professional studio lighting
  • Professional DSLR camera
  • Wide angle lens to capture you and your friends
  • A large selection of props, wigs, hats and quirky items to add to the fun
  • Climate controlled for cool summers and warm winters
  • A beautiful set/back drop to create stunning photographs
  • Simple touch screen operating system
  • High spec, fast photo printer
  • Personalised template for your photo prints
  • Unlimited photo printing
  • Luxury seating area for social media sharing and event guest book
  • Share your photos on Facebook, Twitter, email and SMS*

*The venue must have wi-fi or 3G to enable online social media sharing, email and SMS. If this is not possible we can upload the photos to an event page for you within 48 hours. You will always be able to walk away with our prints.

THE AIRSTREAM PHOTO BOOTH

Airstream Studio is a luxury photo booth experience. Able to host groups of up to 6 people at a time in our beautiful vintage airstream trailer for a unique, fun and social experience. Featuring a professional DSLR camera and studio lighting set up, this isn't just a photo booth, it's a mobile photography studio

Our sets are designed for various different looks from burlesque, vintage or nautical. We welcome commissions to create a theme of your choice. We have an ever growing prop box full of wigs, hats, masks and unique items.

WEDDING GUEST BOOKS

Would you like a special book of memories for your wedding day? Choose a personalised guest book from a range of 6 beautiful designs and your guests can stick their wedding day photos inside and write their personal messages to you. Your photo booth guest book will be available to take away with you on your wedding day.

  

Personalised guest books cost ¬£50 and include pens, glue and stickers, placed our luxury diner style seating area so your guests can convey their blessings for you.
